  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n\r\n## Problem \r\n\r\nSometimes, a chat view stops scrolling and the back button stops responding on iOS if you navigate to a chat and back several times (community channel, 1-1, etc.).\r\nSuch actions as focusing on the input field or swiping to the right (to go back) fix the issue.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nUI doesn't freeze\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nUI partially freezes\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n1. Open a community on an iOS device\r\n2. Open and close a channel several times\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: nightly 16/11\r\n- Operating System: iOS\r\n\r\n",
